*Nevin* skup pozitivne energije čini da se oko njega svi osećaju zaštićeno. (Innocent gathering of positive energy makes everyone around him feel safe.)

*Nevinost* deteta je najčistiji oblik beskrajne ljubavi. (Child's innocence is the purest form of boundless love.)

Ova *nevina* devojčica nikada ne bi izdala svoje najbolje prijatelje. (This innocent girl would never betray her best friends.)

Ona je uživala u *nevinosti* svoje dece. (She was enjoying the innocence of her children.)

*Nevin* je bio iznenađen kada je saznao istinu. (Innocent was surprised when he found out the truth.)